##### Database (required)
ODDISH_DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://oddish:oddish@HOST:5432/oddish

##### LLM API Keys
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=...
OPENAI_API_KEY=s...
GEMINI_API_KEY=...

##### Cloud sandboxes (optional)
DAYTONA_API_KEY=...
MODAL_TOKEN_ID=...
MODAL_TOKEN_SECRET=...

##### S3-compatible storage (required)
# ODDISH_S3_BUCKET=...
# ODDISH_S3_REGION=...
# ODDISH_S3_ACCESS_KEY=...
# ODDISH_S3_SECRET_KEY=y...
# ODDISH_S3_ENDPOINT_URL=...
